Meeting Coordination and Management:
- Send automated meeting invitations with appropriate agenda items and preparation materials
- Coordinate meeting logistics including room reservations, technology setup, and catering requirements
- Track meeting preparation status and send reminders for required documents or presentations
- Monitor meeting attendance and reschedule as needed to ensure key participants are present
- Manage recurring meeting series and adjust schedules based on changing business priorities

